00:37:30,498 --> 00:37:32,250
MAXINE: You too.

762
00:37:32,250 --> 00:37:33,418
Did you do this?

763
00:37:33,418 --> 00:37:34,794
ASHLEY: Yeah.
When the lights went out,

764
00:37:34,794 --> 00:37:36,796
I scooped up some of
Carly's burnt remains,

765
00:37:36,796 --> 00:37:38,756
smeared Kappa Kappa Phi
on all of your foreheads,

766
00:37:38,756 --> 00:37:41,426
in the dark, in 15 seconds
without any of you noticing,

767
00:37:41,426 --> 00:37:42,886
'cause I'm magic.

768
00:37:45,763 --> 00:37:48,224
What? What the hell
are you all looking at?

769
00:37:49,976 --> 00:37:51,936
Why are you all looking at me?

770
00:37:52,937 --> 00:37:55,190
- I strongly suggest
that you tell the truth, Ashley.

771
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:57,025
- No.
