772
00:37:58,276 --> 00:38:00,111
[Ashley screaming]

773
00:38:00,111 --> 00:38:03,114
[running footsteps]

774
00:38:18,046 --> 00:38:21,674
[sobbing]
What is happening?

775
00:38:21,674 --> 00:38:24,010
- Ashley, it's time for you
to tell the truth.

776
00:38:24,010 --> 00:38:26,304
I've seen the video,
and it was you

777
00:38:26,304 --> 00:38:27,805
who told the other girls
to lie,

778
00:38:27,805 --> 00:38:28,806
and look what happened to them.

779
00:38:28,806 --> 00:38:29,849
- I didn't lie.

780
00:38:29,849 --> 00:38:31,893
Your sister died in a fire.

781
00:38:31,893 --> 00:38:34,354
- [eerie whisper]
You lie!

782
00:38:34,354 --> 00:38:38,525
- [gasps]
What is happening?

783
00:38:38,525 --> 00:38:40,610
- Wrong answer.

784
00:38:40,610 --> 00:38:43,321
I can't help you
if you don't help yourself.

785
00:38:43,321 --> 00:38:45,615
- I didn't do anything.
I didn't lie.

786
00:38:45,615 --> 00:38:47,575
What is happening?

787
00:38:47,575 --> 00:38:50,995
[Ashley sobbing and panting]

788
00:38:53,957 --> 00:38:55,750
- [in Laura's voice]:
You've all been marked,

789
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:57,293
and you are now my sisters.

790
00:38:58,711 --> 00:39:02,549
- Ashley, what the hell?

791
00:39:02,549 --> 00:39:03,967
- [in Laura's voice]:
No more hazing,

792
00:39:03,967 --> 00:39:05,385
no more hurting each other,

793
00:39:05,385 --> 00:39:09,722
no more cheating,
and no more lies.

794
00:39:09,722 --> 00:39:11,641
Not in this house.

795
00:39:11,641 --> 00:39:14,894
You are all Kappa Kappa Phi.

796
00:39:14,894 --> 00:39:16,521
[echoing] We are now a family.

797
00:39:16,521 --> 00:39:18,815
And we are loyal to each other.

798
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,568
- Laura.

799
00:39:23,403 --> 00:39:25,113
- Hey, Iggy.

800
00:39:25,113 --> 00:39:28,032
- I knew it was you.
I knew it.

801
00:39:33,121 --> 00:39:34,581
[water splashing softly]

802
00:39:34,581 --> 00:39:37,208
- You remember that summer
when Mom left us all alone?

803
00:39:39,627 --> 00:39:42,088
I hugged you, and you remember
what I said to you.

804
00:39:45,049 --> 00:39:47,594
I said it doesn't matter
who leaves...

805
00:39:47,594 --> 00:39:49,470
It matters who stays.
- It matters who stays.

806
00:39:50,930 --> 00:39:52,724
But you did this.

807
00:39:52,724 --> 00:39:55,518
You killed all of those girls.
Why?

808
00:39:55,518 --> 00:39:56,728
- To protect you.

809
00:39:58,187 --> 00:39:59,606
To protect all of you.

810
00:40:00,898 --> 00:40:03,276
Those girls were monsters, Iggy.

811
00:40:03,276 --> 00:40:06,154
- Laura, your death
was an accident.

812
00:40:06,154 --> 00:40:09,115
- You call the fire an accident?

813
00:40:09,115 --> 00:40:11,200
[electricity sparking]

814
00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:13,786
They set the house on fire
to hide the truth.

815
00:40:13,786 --> 00:40:15,371
Sisters don't lie to each other,

816
00:40:15,371 --> 00:40:17,290
and sisters
don't hurt each other.

817
00:40:17,290 --> 00:40:18,666
- You're right, they shouldn't.

818
00:40:20,126 --> 00:40:22,670
It was out of fear,
and what they did was wrong.

819
00:40:24,005 --> 00:40:25,298
But it wasn't murder.

820
00:40:26,507 --> 00:40:28,801
- How can you defend them,

821
00:40:28,801 --> 00:40:31,638
after you watched
what they did to me,

822
00:40:31,638 --> 00:40:33,139
how they hurt me...

823
00:40:35,141 --> 00:40:37,852
and left me all alone,
and took you from me...

824
00:40:39,354 --> 00:40:40,605
and tore us apart?

825
00:40:40,605 --> 00:40:42,565
What about our pledge, Iggy?

826
00:40:44,192 --> 00:40:45,902
What about you and me?

827
00:40:45,902 --> 00:40:47,862
- When I lost you,

828
00:40:47,862 --> 00:40:50,073
I didn't think I could
ever be whole again.

829
00:40:50,073 --> 00:40:51,699
[Shauna sobbing]

830
00:40:51,699 --> 00:40:55,370
And now you're back,
still protecting me,

831
00:40:55,370 --> 00:40:56,996
even when you're gone.

832
00:40:58,456 --> 00:41:00,291
- I'll always protect you,
kiddo.

833
00:41:01,709 --> 00:41:03,252
- I love you so much.

834
00:41:04,796 --> 00:41:06,923
But I don't need you
to take care of me anymore.

835
00:41:09,050 --> 00:41:11,761
I'm strong because
you were my sister.

836
00:41:14,305 --> 00:41:17,767
Whatever you're going to do,
stop, please. Okay?

837
00:41:17,767 --> 00:41:20,019
No more killing,
not for me.

838
00:41:21,145 --> 00:41:23,356
You have to promise me.

839
00:41:23,356 --> 00:41:25,817
- Okay. I promise.

840
00:41:26,984 --> 00:41:29,487
No more killing...

841
00:41:29,487 --> 00:41:32,281
[water splashing softly]

842
00:41:33,324 --> 00:41:34,909
...after this one.

843
00:41:35,910 --> 00:41:38,204
- Laura, no!

844
00:41:38,204 --> 00:41:40,289
[electricity sparking]

845
00:41:44,502 --> 00:41:45,670
- Shit!

846
00:41:51,759 --> 00:41:53,928
[electricity crackling]

847
00:41:53,928 --> 00:41:56,681
- [water bubbling]
- [Shauna sobbing]

848
00:42:01,310 --> 00:42:02,520
- I'm getting out of here.

849
00:42:05,106 --> 00:42:09,444
- [eerie whisper]
You lie, you die!

850
00:42:09,444 --> 00:42:13,573
<i> You lie, you die!</i>

851
00:42:16,743 --> 00:42:19,704
<i> - [on TV]: After a month
</i>of the entire Greek Row

852
00:42:19,704 --> 00:42:21,664
being shut down,
it's been decided

853
00:42:21,664 --> 00:42:23,624
that Kappa Kappa Phi
sorority house

854
00:42:23,624 --> 00:42:26,085
will remain closed
pending an investigation

855
00:42:26,085 --> 00:42:28,921
into the deaths
of several of its members.

856
00:42:28,921 --> 00:42:33,593
That said, ahem, parties
broke out everywhere

857
00:42:33,593 --> 00:42:37,346
when it was announced that the
rest of Greek Row can reopen.

858
00:42:37,346 --> 00:42:39,056
[cheering and shouting]

859
00:42:39,056 --> 00:42:40,808
Okay. Obviously,
cut the last part.

860
00:42:40,808 --> 00:42:44,395
And get the hell out of here.
Fucking frat boys.

861
00:42:44,395 --> 00:42:46,814
[♪♪♪]

862
00:42:46,814 --> 00:42:49,567
- I mean, I think
it's the right thing.

863
00:42:49,567 --> 00:42:51,569
- VOICE: [eerie whisper]
You lie...

864
00:42:51,569 --> 00:42:55,198
You know, no one should ever
go into that house again.

865
00:42:55,198 --> 00:42:56,741
- Uh-huh.

866
00:42:56,741 --> 00:43:00,953
- I love her, but my hope is
that they tear that house down.

867
00:43:03,247 --> 00:43:06,083
Sorry, am I still talking?
You must--

868
00:43:06,083 --> 00:43:08,669
you must think
I'm a crazy person.

869
00:43:08,669 --> 00:43:10,922
- I absolutely do not.

870
00:43:13,424 --> 00:43:16,511
- Stewart! Did you hear
anything I just said?

871
00:43:16,511 --> 00:43:18,012
Are you just pretending
to listen to me

872
00:43:18,012 --> 00:43:19,764
so you can hook up with me?

873
00:43:19,764 --> 00:43:20,973
- No.

874
00:43:20,973 --> 00:43:23,559
- VOICE: [eerie whisper]
You lie...

875
00:43:23,559 --> 00:43:26,354
- You're not lying, are you?

876
00:43:26,354 --> 00:43:27,563
- Noooo!

877
00:43:30,149 --> 00:43:32,401
Sex is the last thing
on my mind.

878
00:43:34,737 --> 00:43:35,738
- Okay.

879
00:43:36,739 --> 00:43:39,075
- [creaking]
- [thud]

880
00:43:39,075 --> 00:43:40,243
[Shauna screaming]

881
00:43:40,243 --> 00:43:43,246
[song playing]

882
00:44:08,604 --> 00:44:11,607
[♪♪♪]